What we can do to help

Africa has enough creative, intelligent, and passionate kids – and if we can be more supportive so that they can concentrate internally on how to bring their talents to life, we could change the entire eradication agenda. The world would be a change for good.

We’ve got to find a way to end cycle of poverty, violence, ignorance, and disease and if we’re looking to find a pocket of hope – it can be found in the future of youth like Ezo. Invest your strengths in the youth and our world will experience a new sustainable revolution.

– Chika George Andrew

Let’s have your thoughts on poverty, money, and youth in Africa otherwise known as the problem of next generation
